{"success":true,"result":{"Q_10108810205081-1":{"resources":[],"questions":[{"id":"Q_10108810205081-1","subjectId":101,"knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[{"id":"TM_10100000673226","main":1}],"solutionMethods":[],"resourceIds":null,"resourceIndex":0,"listenUrl":null,"listenName":null,"listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"paperIds":["P_10100124478595-1"],"books":null,"booksNew":null,"contentTypeId":1010008,"contentType2Id":0,"difficultyInt":3,"description":"阅读文章，回答问题","notFitMobile":0,"seconds":45,"complex":1,"nid":null,"lastEditorId":null,"finalAuditorId":null,"roughAuditorIds":null,"content":{"content":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>智斗</strong></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">聂耳生来性格开朗，幽默乐观，机智勇敢。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">1929年，他在昆明参加共青团活动时，就以机智勇敢而闻名。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">有一次，共青团员出去贴标语，别人都找僻静的街巷去贴，聂耳却专门往熙熙攘攘的人群里钻。①<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">他看见一个大个子警察在人群中耀武扬威地走来走去，就分开人群走上前去在警察背上拍了一下，笑着说：“老总辛苦了！”</span>不一会儿，许多人都注视着大个子警察的背后。愚蠢的警察感到莫名其妙，往背后一摸，发现贴着一张标语，这才恍然大悟，知道是聂耳的“杰作”。可是聂耳早已消失得无影无踪了。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">聂耳智斗特务的故事，就更有趣了。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">那是在1934年，3月15日是我国著名戏剧家田汉的36岁生日。田汉的好友夏衍、阳翰笙等人秘密集会庆祝，聂耳也带着小提琴来了。不知何故，这事引起了特务的注意。正当他们开怀畅谈之际，突然响起了一阵急促的敲门声，紧接着闯进两个陌生人。大家用眼神互相打了个招呼，各自会意<span style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">。②</span><span style=\"text-indent: 2em; text-decoration: underline;\">这时，只见聂耳拿起小提琴，对着两个陌生人反复演奏下面的音调：</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">34－3－15－36</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">聂耳围着这两个陌生人绕圈子，边拉边唱，大家也随着唱起了莫名其妙的音调。两个陌生人以为这是一帮醉鬼，转身走了。</p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: none;\">③</span><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">聂耳赶紧把门关上，冲着大家做了个鬼脸。</span>这时，大家问道：“聂耳，你刚才演奏的是什么？”④<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">聂耳神秘地笑了笑，说：“这是鄙人的即兴创作。‘34－3－15－36’就是‘34年3月15日36岁’的意思。”</span></p><p style=\"text-indent: 2em;\">大家听了哈哈大笑，原来是聂耳与特务面对面地庆祝田汉的生日，真是令人开心！</p>","contentDesc":"","analysis":"","subContents":[{"content":"<p>文中点明文章主旨的一句话是（　）。</p>","answers":[{"answer":"0","subAnswers":[],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null}],"subContentTypeId":1,"analysis":"","optionType":"sentence","options":[{"option":"聂耳生来性格开朗，幽默乐观，机智勇敢。","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}},{"option":"聂耳智斗特务的故事，就更有趣了。","file":{"fileId":"","url":"","filename":"","seconds":0}}],"hideOptionNumber":0,"listenUrl":"","listenName":"","listenSeconds":0,"exploreSeconds":0,"answersSeconds":0,"oralDict":{"seconds":null,"variables":null,"keywords":null,"options":null,"voiceText":null,"sentencePatterns":null,"picUrl":null,"picName":null,"beginListenUrl":null,"endListenUrl":null,"scorePercentage":null,"readySeconds":null,"listenFile":null,"contentDesc":null,"answers":null,"voiceTextsNew":null,"jsgf":null,"videoUrl":null,"videoCoverUrl":null,"highlightPos":null},"submitWays":[0],"tags":[101007],"analysisList":null,"pictureUrl":"","extras":{},"tagsDesc":["其他"]},{"content":"<p>分别选出文中画线的句子是用什么表现方法刻画了聂耳怎样的特点。</p><p>①__$$__　②__$$__　③__$$__　④__$$__</p>","answers":[{"answer":"1","subAnswers":[],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null},{"answer":"2","subAnswers":[],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null},{"answer":"3","subAnswers":[],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[],"solutionMethods":[],"classificationListenUrl":null},{"answer":"0","subAnswers":[],"richTexts":null,"scorePercentage":1,"classification":"","knowledgePoints":null,"knowledgePointsNew":[],"testMethods":[],"solutionMethods